      "value": "<p>Category: Archetype</p><p>Archetype: Genjutsu Specialist</p><p>Prerequisite: Illusionist Training, Level 10+</p><p> </p><p>You have continued to train to better master the art of Genjutsu. </p><p>This training has culminated into you being defined as an Expert. </p><p><br />• You gain 1 additional Actualization Die. </p><p>• You learn one Malleable Mirage that you qualify for, as if you were a 5th level Genjutsu Specialist. </p><p>• Select one effect granted by Real World Conversion. <br />You gain the chosen ability.</p>",
